{"tid":1639670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Pornhub 做戰線有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T16:46:27.000Z","uid":296536,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdb51bd896ca15c0046f543cc0b8af55db7cdfb","tid":1639670,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:32:29.000Z","msg":"見到各大社交平台都有咁多五毛留言，呢幾日仲有幾單因為大陸人亂講野做左國際戰線材料，我就發覺有時根本唔洗我地旁述，五毛講野本身就足以令外國人反感。<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時聽過個數據，話3分1定4分1網上搜尋都係關於Porn, 如果運用到呢啲平台就容易connect 到好多人。但係文宣要點做呢？如果段段片留個Liberate Hong Kong, Hong Kong is not China 宣傳太唔吸引，亦都容易令人反感，所以我諗到嘅就係引戰。<br />\n<br />\n根據小弟多年打丁經驗，Pornhub 其實都好多大陸殘體留言，呢個趨勢有增無減，而我觀察之中，最多大陸留言係日本同中國嘅片，可以嘗試用瀏覽量多又有呢啲留言嘅片入手。<br />\n<br />\n大概回應內容我諗到以下嘅：<br />\n1. Wondering why so many Chinese comments these days <br />\n2. Just realized Chinese can access Pornhub<br />\n3. Thought that China had banned porns... <br />\n<br />\n仲未實測過唔知有冇用，大家覺得有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4961e3f489e1ea56fc301974d491d98e865dbec2","tid":1639670,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"P 牌慘過三等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63b15b854123dc5521522e98d7b56ccecb421ea","tid":1639670,"uid":296536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"扮推得郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153f0a9da4e6580fe9e919bf5940e0b966b8d7aa","tid":1639670,"uid":203444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3796d71d9ee4595c5f7173d815ca36dd6f30f5f","tid":1639670,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"啲片唔關事會好快被官方del"},{"pid":"29148d82ed5d4c3f2f52a8a522b2e49a155159fd","tid":1639670,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"